Unapologetically proud of my son Jasper A. Marsalis & promoting his highly-anticipated debut album, EXCELSIOR, out this Friday on renowned label Warp Records, Slauson Malone 1 unveils his final preview of the record with new single "Half-Life." (Watch on YouTube) 🔥🔥🔥

EXCELSIOR has already received early praise ahead of its release with The New York Times describing it as "deeply ambitious, engaging and full of winning eccentricities," and Pitchfork recently calling it one of the most anticipated releases coming this fall.

The single is a poignant exploration of the aftermath of a heart-wrenching breakup and the intricate dynamics of falling out of love. Much like the concept of nuclear half-life, it delves into the idea that one never entirely ceases to love someone; instead, that love gradually diminishes, halving itself with the passage of time.
